---
title: Chargrilled Chimichurri Beef & Grilled Veggie Salad with Cheesy Flatbreads & Salsa Verde
description: The weather is nice so the next natural step is to fire up that grill! Gather up the troops and put on a BBQ spread of seared
chimichurri beef rump, grilled veggies freshened with a salsa verde to lighten the palette. Don’t forget to grab a few garlic
flatbreads to soak up the aioli.
